          "Experience our state-of-the-art treatments in a safe, comfortable environment. Our expert team uses advanced techniques and premium products to deliver optimal results. Each procedure is performed with precision and care, ensuring your comfort throughout the process. We'll guide you through each step, making sure you feel confident and informed.",
        icon: 'tabler:ribbon-health',
